    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            DisableJudgmentGroup();
            $("input[id$='ButtonSearch']").click(function () {
                var screenOK = checkTaxMap();
                TrimEntryFields();
                if (screenOK == false) {
                    alert("Error on tax map search: A from and through value must be entered when searching for a range.");
                    return false;
                }
                screenOK = checkDateType();
                if (screenOK == false) {
                    alert("Date searches require a date type combined with a valid beginning and/or ending date");
                    return false;
                }
                screenOK = checkRequiredFields();
                if (screenOK == false) {
                    alert("A Last Name, Case Number, CDR Code, Indictment Number, Date or Tax Map Number is required.");
                    return false;
                }
                return true;
            });
            $("select[id$='DropDownListDateFilter']").change(function () {
                var screenOK = ClearDates();
                return true;
            });

            $("input[id$='RadioButtonIndexAll']").change(function () {
                var screenOK = DisableJudgmentGroup();
                return true;
            });
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonLisPendens']").change(function () {
                var screenOK = DisableJudgmentGroup();
                return true;
            });
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgments']").change(function () {
                var screenOK = EnableJudgmentGroup();
                return true;
            });

        });

        function checkTaxMap() {
            var tmTo = $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapTo']").val();
            var tmFrom = $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapFrom']").val();
            var tmValid = true;
            if (tmTo > "") {
                if (tmFrom == "") {
                    tmValid = false;
                }
            }
            return tmValid;
        }

        function checkDateType() {
            var dBegin = new Date($("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val());
            var dEnd = new Date($("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val());
            var dType = $("select[id$='DropDownListDateFilter'] option:selected").text();
            var dValid = false;
            if ((dType == "") && ($("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val() == "") && ($("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val() == "")) {
                return true;
            }
            if (dType > "") {
                if (dBegin > "") {
                    dValid = true;
                }
                if (dEnd > "") {
                    dValid = true;
                }
            }
            if (dBegin > "") {
                if (dType > "") {
                    dValid = true;
                }
            }
            if (dEnd > "") {
                if (dType > "") {
                    dValid = true;
                }
            }
            if (dValid == true) {
                if (dBegin > dEnd) {
                    dValid = false;
                }
            }

            return dValid;
        }

        function checkRequiredFields() {
            var somethingEntered = false;
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxCaseNumber']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxlastName']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapFrom']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapTo']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxCDRCode']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            if ($("input[id$='TextBoxIndNum']").val() > "") {
                return true;
            }
            return somethingEntered;
        }

        function ClearDates() {
            if ($("select[id$='DropDownListDateFilter'] option:selected").text() == "") {
                $("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val("");
                $("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val("");
            }
            return true;
        }

        function TrimEntryFields() {

            $("input[id$='TextBoxCaseNumber']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxCaseNumber']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxlastName']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxlastName']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxFirstname']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxFirstname']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxMiddleName']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxMiddleName']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxSuffix']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxSuffix']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapFrom']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapFrom']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapTo']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapTo']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val()));
            $("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val(trimString($("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val()));

            return true;
        }
        function ClearSearchFields() {
            $("input[id$='TextBoxCaseNumber']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxlastName']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxFirstname']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxMiddleName']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxSuffix']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapFrom']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxTaxMapTo']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxDateFrom']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxDateTo']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxCDRCode']").val("");
            $("input[id$='TextBoxIndNum']").val("");

            $("select[id$='DropDownListCourtType']").get(0).selectedIndex = 0;
            $("select[id$='DropdownlistCaseSubType']").get(0).selectedIndex = 0;
            $("select[id$='DropDownListParties']").get(0).selectedIndex = 0;
            $("select[id$='DropdownlistActionCode']").get(0).selectedIndex = 0;
            $("select[id$='DropDownListDateFilter']").get(0).selectedIndex = 0;

            $("input[id$='RadioButtonIndexAll']").attr('checked', 'checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonLisPendens']").removeAttr('checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgments']").removeAttr('checked');

            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonAll']").attr('checked', 'checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementFor']").removeAttr('checked');

            $("input[id$='RadioButtonNameBeginsWith']").attr('checked', 'checked');
            $("input[id$='RadioButtonNameContains']").removeAttr('checked');
            return true;
        }

        function DisableJudgmentGroup() {
            if (!$("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgments']:checked").val()) {
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonAll']").attr('checked', 'checked');
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementFor']").removeAttr('checked');
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementAgainst']").removeAttr('checked');
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonAll']").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementFor']").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
                $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementAgainst']").attr('disabled', 'disabled');
            }
            return true;
        }

        function EnableJudgmentGroup() {
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonAll']").attr('checked', 'checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementFor']").removeAttr('checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementAgainst']").removeAttr('checked');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonAll']").removeAttr('disabled');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementFor']").removeAttr('disabled');
            $("input[id$='RadiobuttonJudgementAgainst']").removeAttr('disabled');
            return true;
        }
        function fDisplayHelp(surl) {
            window.open(surl, "PublicIndexHelp", "width=800,height=600,toolbar=no,location=no,directories=no,status=no,menubar=no,scrollbars=yes,copyhistory=no,resizable=yes");
            return false;
        }

        function trimString(wrkString) {
            return wrkString.replace(/^\s\s*/, '').replace(/\s\s*$/, '');
        }

        function hidemodal() {
            $find('mpeBID').hide();
            return false;
        }

        function hidealertmodal() {
            $find('mpeSealedCaseAlert').hide();
            return false;
        }

        function showalertmodal() {
            $find('mpeSealedCaseAlert').show();
            return false;
        }

    </script>
